prodNameC: 美堅希堤亞安非他命試劑
ingredientsDesc:
EA Reconstitution Buffer: Contains piperazine-N, N-bis [2-ethanesulfonic
acid], buffer salts, stabilizer, and preservative.
EA Reagent: Contains 0.156 g/L Enzyme acceptor, 7.081 mg/L monoclonal
antibodies to d-amphetamine and 7.081 mg/L monoclonal antibodies to d-methamphetamine, buffer
salts, detergent, and preservative.
ED Reconstitution Buffer: Contains piperazine-N, N-bis [2-ethanesulfonic acid]
buffer; buffer salts, and preservative.
ED Reagent: Contains 7.12 μg/L Enzyme Donor conjugated to d-amphetamine and
11.3 μg/L Enzyme Donor conjugated to d-methamphetamine, 1.67g/L chlorophenol
red-ß-D-galactopyranoside, stabilizer, and preservative.
applicantName: 醫全實業股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市大安區和平東路二段107巷23之9號2樓
efficacy: 定性或半定量分析人體尿液中的安非他命。
